{"tid":2414493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我建議，一旦留言因負評過多而屏蔽，該留言產生的整個討論串都屏蔽","createTime":"2021-02-19T12:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T14:03:16.000Z","uid":267881,"like":19,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"75258a998a14fc0324af950caa4d35a91d3d29de","tid":2414493,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:27:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">點解要提出新建議？</span><br />\n五毛PR橫行，頭幾個留言經常被佢哋利用黎帶風向，之前嘅建議俾admin無視：<br />\n[size=1]<em>收咗大量建議同1000+正評，正式向admin提出新系統「！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194338</a></em>[/size=2]<br />\n既然admin唔肯標籤佢哋，所以我再提出新建議：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「一旦留言因負評過多而屏蔽<br />\n該留言產生的整個討論串都屏蔽」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">新系統會影響咩人？</span><br />\n好多user唔係常駐連登，亦唔可能每次都睇名起底先回覆，或者明知都忍唔住回，當佢地回覆的留言被屏蔽後，自己個回覆都會被一齊屏蔽。受益人會係想正常討論或追post嘅user。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">咩種類嘅討論串會被屏蔽？</span><br />\n負評多到被屏蔽嘅留言通常都係五毛言論、驚嚇圖，或者純粹係on9言論，呢啲留言往往係最吸引到其他user回覆，回覆內容全部都係恥笑/ 謾罵，甚至演化成罵戰，為啖氣，明嘅，你有你屏蔽住咁嘈，其他人唔使被迫睇罵戰。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">點解要屏蔽成個討論串？</span><br />\n一個留言負評多到被屏蔽，證明係非常令人反感、對該主題冇意義，所以引申出來嘅回覆都會係冇意義，重複又重複嘅恥笑/ 謾罵只會破壞正常討論，追post都唔暢順，所以全部屏蔽晒可以令討論重回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">會唔會破壞言論自由？</span><br />\n唔會，呢個系統冇禁止任何人發表任何言論，然後任何人都可以閱讀該言論，分別只係㩒個制。<br />\n冇user會被永久標籤，系統係針對留言內容唔係針對人，係一次性效果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位點睇？"},{"pid":"012132857df5816c5e7339d9a1e78cdee871d00a","tid":2414493,"uid":13160,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"你梗係想俾人負評啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9636f7d5ecf8089aff74c33a3eb1d125d21ce707","tid":2414493,"uid":267881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"012132857df5816c5e7339d9a1e78cdee871d00a","tid":2414493,"uid":13160,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"你梗係想俾人負評啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:31:24.000Z","msg":"救救連登"},{"pid":"572fb729d5efd593c0415a85ddf02b42498a5b4b","tid":2414493,"uid":13160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9636f7d5ecf8089aff74c33a3eb1d125d21ce707","tid":2414493,"uid":267881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"012132857df5816c5e7339d9a1e78cdee871d00a","tid":2414493,"uid":13160,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:29:38.000Z","msg":"你梗係想俾人負評啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:31:24.000Z","msg":"救救連登"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"Ok 幫推"},{"pid":"d75031c76d3864bb94ed0b2c553bc75d74d84d52","tid":2414493,"uid":84783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"腐皮有時係用黎投票wor, ching"},{"pid":"7b1576cd070be0baa361167a01d907a849c52ba1","tid":2414493,"uid":4213,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n最好就咩都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係係係<br />\n我講野難聽<br />\n我係五毛<br />\nblock我啦<br />\nblock完你個同溫層又會加強左<br />\n變到同班藍絲一樣<br />\n得返一面睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1268c8f0663ddf917e1846e358e5887e13e4a6f5","tid":2414493,"uid":343017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"PR+網軍多到可以洗負皮..."},{"pid":"8afa417577dae8a648cadf1b9d1de122907a73ec","tid":2414493,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d75031c76d3864bb94ed0b2c553bc75d74d84d52","tid":2414493,"uid":84783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"腐皮有時係用黎投票wor, ching"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"開帖頂樓唔會屏蔽，留言先會<br />\n就算因為咁蔽咗，都唔會阻到討論<br />\n唔回覆投票嗰個留言咪得"},{"pid":"c039b6eefc2a6bfd4b768939bac33e46aeed1975","tid":2414493,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1268c8f0663ddf917e1846e358e5887e13e4a6f5","tid":2414493,"uid":343017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"PR+網軍多到可以洗負皮..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"有冇例子？"},{"pid":"b5b4722172bf371b8dbbf38d6b427d6daf942a79","tid":2414493,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"老實講睇唔明你個topic<br />\n唔知邊忽係廣東話"},{"pid":"7321720f9d025104d1ac97d0a8238743121dedd4","tid":2414493,"uid":63452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"幾多負皮為之過多？100？500？1000？定總正皮嘅50％？<br />\n有啲post 唔多人入，用實數cutoff 未必過，用relative 可以10 個負皮就被ban，成個thread 空白一片<br />\n<br />\n同埋有時大家俾正負皮會有跟風趨勢，到左，之後先會有人平反，然後就會正皮多過負皮。咁呢啲case 又點？<br />\n<br />\n同埋條rule 係邊個區執行？成個連登執行嘅會影響其他非政治討論。只係係時事台嘅，走去波台開post 你都吹佢唔漲<br />\n<br />\n雖然我憎熱狗奶共，但係熱狗支持者唔係五毛。連登依家都普遍反熱狗，佢地啲comment 實俾人負皮多。咁係咪佢地嘅言論就唔係言論？<br />\n<br />\n假設條rule 真係實行，PR 控制言論就會俾以前更容易，因為人海戰術會變左100％ 成功"},{"pid":"99f21f441d26a66c1c106705318c32d60e87c5fa","tid":2414493,"uid":40415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:08:28.000Z","msg":"屏蔽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13c84f34f01f6b0da76e4a512bd8d094c514468","tid":2414493,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:09:54.000Z","msg":"屌 到時成個波台都blocked post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19df1e301933b88de10f481520aedb9b60215ef1","tid":2414493,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed116801c797f30f8aa00e3e90b2ff7d6ba31b4","tid":241449